text: ahasda, bhumiyada utpadanaya kala aya, ættenma ohuma, (yam kisivak utpadanaya kirimata adahas kara) “vanu!” yayi ohu kiyana davase, evelema eya sidu vanneya. ohuge vacanaya satyayayi. sur pimbinu labana dinadi, balaya ohutama ayat vanu æta. gupta dæyada, elidarav dæyada ohu hondin danneya. ohu gnanavantayeku vasayenda, (siyalla) hondin danneku vasayenda sitinneya
